config KV_CPU
	tristate "KV-CPU Reference Control Plane Driver"
	depends on PCI
	help
	  Say Y here if you want to support the KV-CPU AI memory accelerator.
	  This driver provides a control plane for LLM inference semantics
	  such as decode steps and KV-block lifecycle hints.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the
	  module will be called kv_cpu.
